kquote><br />\n有冇人真係會J家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩慘得過畀自己細佬話唔正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你係唔正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話我唔會好似我啲男仔friend覺得你好索囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad20b440d1cd08001ad1545dff710ab1f2e732a8","tid":228734,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T07:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}